    <pre>The next step here is too make a tarball of the python-openid code with the
updates in that pull request. Then update our setup.py to point at that version,
and run:

 ./bin/buildout

and watch to see if it gets the new version (that you tarball'd up) of
python-openid.

If so, and if that makes this error go away, then I will happily copy that
tarball to <a href="http://linode.openhatch.org/~paulproteus/">http://linode.openhatch.org/~paulproteus/</a> and merge a patch to
setup.py! That would close this bug.</pre>
