  </tr>
  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>A user tried to sign in with an OpenID web page that has UTF-8 characters in it. 

To reproduce:

Send a POST to /openid/signin/ with this data:

POST: {'action': 'verify', 'openid_url':
'<a href="http://www.columbia.edu/kermit/utf8.html">http://www.columbia.edu/kermit/utf8.html</a>', 'next': ''}

(You can use any utf-8 page, I think.)

Next step: See if someone can reproduce this bug, hopefully with an automated test.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
